      <h2>How To Build The Android APK</h2>
      <p>Follow these professional steps to convert this website into a Play Store ready Android application.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-box" style="max-width:1000px;margin:auto;">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:20px;color:#0b5ed7;">STEP 1 — Upload Website Online</h3>
      <p style="line-height:1.9;color:#555;">
        Upload this HTML website to:
        <br><br>
        • GitHub Pages
        <br>
        • Netlify
        <br>
        • Vercel
        <br>
        • cPanel Hosting
        <br><br>
        Example Website:
        <br>
        https://smarttots.netlify.app
      </p>

      <h3 style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#0b5ed7;">STEP 2 — Create Android App Using Android Studio</h3>
      <p style="line-height:1.9;color:#555;">
        1. Install Android Studio
        <br>
        2. Create New Project → Empty Activity
        <br>
        3. Name: Smart Tots School
        <br>
        4. Package Name: com.smarttots.school
        <br>
        5. Minimum SDK: Android 7+
      </p>

      <h3 style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#0b5ed7;">STEP 3 — Add WebView Code</h3>

      <div style="background:#0f172a;color:#fff;padding:25px;border-radius:20px;overflow:auto;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;">
&lt;WebView
    android:id="@+id/webView"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent" /&gt;
      </div>

      <div style="background:#0f172a;color:#fff;padding:25px;border-radius:20px;overflow:auto;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin-top:20px;">
webView.getSettings().setJavaScriptEnabled(true);
webView.loadUrl("https://smarttots.netlify.app");
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#0b5ed7;">STEP 4 — Add School Branding</h3>
      <p style="line-height:1.9;color:#555;">
        Add:
        <br>
        • School Logo
        <br>
        • Splash Screen
        <br>
        • App Icon
        <br>
        • School Name
        <br>
        • Theme Colors
      </p>

      <h3 style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#0b5ed7;">STEP 5 — Build APK</h3>
      <p style="line-height:1.9;color:#555;">
        Android Studio → Build → Generate Signed Bundle/APK → APK
      </p>

      <h3 style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:20px;color:#0b5ed7;">STEP 6 — Publish To Google Play Store</h3>
      <p style="line-height:1.9;color:#555;">
        Create:
        <br>
        • Google Play Console Account
        <br>
        • App Screenshots
        <br>
        • Privacy Policy
        <br>
        • App Description
        <br>
        • Upload AAB/APK File
      </p>

      <div style="margin-top:40px;padding:30px;background:#e8f3ff;border-radius:25px;">
        <h3 style="color:#0b5ed7;margin-bottom:15px;">Recommended Features For Final APK</h3>
        <ul style="line-height:2;color:#444;padding-left:20px;">
